{"tid":354773,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"失平衡滾落扶手電梯　荃灣站男子血流披面","createTime":"2017-08-10T17:47:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-08-11T11:57:39.000Z","uid":20933,"like":1,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"fa6e60c3dad2bf01a24ff63faa64168eefcdc4f4","tid":354773,"uid":20933,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:47:13.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/media/article/111221/thumbnail/00a19a40b5a2dbfd2a1442fbb7335678.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fmedia%2Farticle%2F111221%2Fthumbnail%2F00a19a40b5a2dbfd2a1442fbb7335678.jpg&h=c106b383&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n男子滾落扶手梯受傷血流披面。<br />\n<br />\n事發於港鐵荃灣站，晚上約10時20分，一名男子乘搭扶手電梯，擬落月台乘坐地鐵時，途中失去平衡突然滾下梯級直達地面，旁人見狀馬上按停扶手電梯，查看男子傷勢，赫見他血流披面，馬上尋找救援。<br />\n<br />\n數分鐘後港鐵職員趕至急救包紮，幸男子神志清醒，僅臉部受傷，由職員協助止血。"},{"pid":"bdecbdfd10e0342ecb2504df6e788413b3866e38","tid":354773,"uid":36383,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:49:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />咁慘，有時搭電梯冇捉扶手都會覺得個人有啲失平衡"},{"pid":"6cae51610c8dd641d8ffda9f536873c89d44b3f0","tid":354773,"uid":36049,"like":1,"dislike":3,"score":-2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:49:56.000Z","msg":"渣ga"},{"pid":"0f5a990be61a2f641dbd1d868801a6ed8714168f","tid":354773,"uid":59898,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:50:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />做咩呀"},{"pid":"5a914e80919b61a5904e2a8c04a2d8937c74e714","tid":354773,"uid":17081,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T17:54:05.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://i2.kknews.cc/large/128100004d56066d3dba\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fi2.kknews.cc%2Flarge%2F128100004d56066d3dba&h=17ac5ae5&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"8113f27da0206c28cd4d1e6fb2a2ae537701a675","tid":354773,"uid":114097,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-08-10T1